movies.title: Mabel
movies.plot: Proving that age is only a number, 99 year old Mabel Sawhill continues to run her catering business in the Maryland and D.C. area. Mabel hosts events that number anywhere from 30 to 1,000 attendees, doing all her own driving, shopping, and cooking. She is a genuine testament for active aging!
